<SYNC Start=1061553><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1061587><P Class=KRCC>
종양도 없고,
<SYNC Start=1063071><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1063106><P Class=KRCC>
