<SYNC Start=1380375><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1380410><P Class=KRCC>
팔을 움켜잡았는데...
<SYNC Start=1382127><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1383713><P Class=KRCC>
죽은 피부 한거풀이 
<SYNC Start=1385997><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1386049><P Class=KRCC>
